{"id":1660741,"retrievedAt":"2026-03-31T12:09:47.800Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1660741,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["CL"],"original_language":"es","original_title":"O’Brien: Las edades del hombre","overview":"After recording the influential album \"Fictions\" in the 1960s with Los Vidrios Quebrados, a true gem of early Chilean rock, Juan Mateo O'Brien didn't sing again for almost 50 years. \"O'Brien: The Ages of Man\" reveals the past, present, and future of one of the founders of creative rock in Chile, through fragments of a puzzle that intersects Santiago, Paris, revolution, exile, music, and words. A keen observer of the local psyche, O'Brien wanders through a constantly transforming city. With a central role for the songs from the album \"Gran Avenida\" - his celebrated recording comeback driven by a new generation - \"O'Brien: The Ages of Man\" is an unusual portrait of a particular protagonist of the 20th century, architect of his own destiny.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/otil0AtQNNuCKIKZGO92PXTOLFf.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"","revenue":0,"runtime":50,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Spanish","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"O’Brien: Las edades del hombre","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6106909,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Juan Mateo O’Brien","original_name":"Juan Mateo O’Brien","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":4,"character":"","credit_id":"69caf118b66db6f5f963762c","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1365100,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Luis Alarcón","original_name":"Luis Alarcón","popularity":0.2722,"profile_path":"/klWB4qQgqK2hqYzLi3urKjHc8H6.jpg","cast_id":5,"character":"","credit_id":"69caf13121d9014c7a5af470","order":